.container {
    display: inline-block;
    width: 333px;
    height: 60px;
    font-size: 16px;
    border: 1px solid #00bebe;
}
.text-ellipsis {
    overflow: hidden;
    text-overflow: ellipsis;
    white-space: nowrap;
}
.text-ellipsis-multi {
    line-height: 20px;
    overflow: hidden;
    text-overflow: ellipsis;
    display: -webkit-box;
    -webkit-line-clamp: 3;  // 
    -webkit-box-orient: vertical
}
```

